sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MRCtrl as ModelRegistryReconciler
    participant MCCtrl as ModelCatalogReconciler
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant REST as rest-container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Client as API Client

    Note over User,PG: Flow 1: Model Registry Instance Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply ModelRegistry CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | User credentials
    K8sAPI->>MutWH: Mutate request<br/>HTTPS/9443 | API server mTLS
    MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Defaulted CR<br/>(DB config, kube-rbac-proxy, OAuth→KRBP migration)
    K8sAPI->>ValWH: Validate request<br/>HTTPS/9443 | API server mTLS
    ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Admission response<br/>(namespace check, unique name, DB config)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created/updated

    K8sAPI->>MRCtrl: Watch event: ModelRegistry CR
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(rest-container + kube-rbac-proxy)
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service (8443/TCP)
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create SA, Role, RoleBinding
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Route (reencrypt TLS)
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Group (OpenShift)
    MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>(system:auth-delegator)
    opt Auto-provision PostgreSQL
        MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create PostgreSQL Deployment + Service + PVC
    end

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 2: Model Registry REST API Access (with kube-rbac-proxy)

    Client->>Router: GET/POST /api/model_registry/...<br/>HTTPS/443 | Bearer token
    Router->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS reencrypt
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443 | Verify user can GET Service
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed/Denied
    KRBP->>REST: Proxy request<br/>HTTP/8080 | localhost (no auth)
    REST->>PG: Query metadata<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 | Username/password
    PG-->>REST: Query results
    REST-->>KRBP: JSON response
    KRBP-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 3: Model Catalog Service

    Client->>Router: GET /api/model_catalog/...<br/>HTTPS/443 | Bearer token
    Router->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS reencrypt
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443 | Verify user can GET catalog Service
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed/Denied
    KRBP->>REST: Proxy to catalog container<br/>HTTP/8080 | localhost
    REST->>PG: Query catalog DB<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 | Username/password (Secret)
    PG-->>REST: Catalog data
    REST-->>KRBP: JSON response
    KRBP-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>Client: JSON response
